<IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" WIDTH=115></TD><TD ALIGN=LEFT BACKGROUND="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/NavigationRightTrim.jpg"><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" WIDTH=15></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN=CENTER><DIV CLASS="Main"><TABLE  BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=6 CELLSPACING=0  WIDTH="100%"><TR><TD  VALIGN="TOP"><center><form name=search action=show_archives.php method=POST><b>Search for string:  <input type=text name=search_string  > <input type=submit name=search_by_string value=Search></form><form name=search_date action=show_archives.php><b>Archived news for the week of:<br><select name=month><option value=1>January</option><option value=2>February</option><option value=3>March</option><option value=4>April</option><option value=5>May</option><option value=6>June</option><option value=7>July</option><option value=8>August</option><option value=9>September</option><option value=10>October</option><option value=11>November</option><option value=12 selected>December</option></select> <select name=day><option value=1>1</option><option value=2>2</option><option value=3>3</option><option value=4>4</option><option value=5>5</option><option value=6 selected>6</option><option value=7>7</option><option value=8>8</option><option value=9>9</option><option value=10>10</option><option value=11>11</option><option value=12>12</option><option value=13>13</option><option value=14>14</option><option value=15>15</option><option value=16>16</option><option value=17>17</option><option value=18>18</option><option value=19>19</option><option value=20>20</option><option value=21>21</option><option value=22>22</option><option value=23>23</option><option value=24>24</option><option value=25>25</option><option value=26>26</option><option value=27>27</option><option value=28>28</option><option value=29>29</option><option value=30>30</option><option value=31>31</option></select> <select name=year><option value=2004 selected>2004</option></select> <input type=submit value=Go></form><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Fri 03 Dec 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="3915"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Topic of the Week - Has your guild had to adapt to changing times lately?</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=3915>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=3915">Mail News</a></span><br>This week our topic of the week asks "Has your guild had to adapt to changing times lately?"  Not sure what this means?  Think i'm insane?  Dead on?  Voice your thoughts <a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/message.asp?topic=79733426&replies=0">right over here</a>.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Fri 03 Dec 2004</span><br><br><br><a name="3914"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Zone Revamps: Splitpaw and Mistmoore</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=3914>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=3914">Mail News</a></span><br>EQ Live has an article up describing some of the upcoming changes to Splitpaw and Mistmoore that will hit Legends the 15th, and all other servers Janurary.  Here's a clip of the Mistmoore article:<blockquote>In Mistmoore's Catacombs, the servants of the Trueborn, a sect of vampires with Mayong Mistmoore's blood flowing through their veins, grew tired of their masters throwing them into the fray against the Norrathian intruders. They came to desire more power for themselves.<br><br>It was not long before the first words of dissension crept through the catacombs on the will of whispers. The Trueborn servants congregated in dark, musty halls away from the eyes of their masters and over time their numbers grew along with their ambitions. Their time had come and soon they would rise up to claim their rightful place in Mistmoore Castle, gaining accolades from Lord Mayong Mistmoore himself for their brilliance and bravery -- or so they supposed.</blockquote><br>You can check out the full article with screenshots for Mistmoore <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/news_section/newsview.jsp?story=64379">here</a> and the Splitpaw article <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/news_section/newsview.jsp?story=64380">here</a>.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Fri 03 Dec 2004</span><br><br><br><a name="3912"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Freaky Friday 12/3/04</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=3912>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=3912">Mail News</a></span><br>This weeks Freaky Friday over on the official boards has a new screenshot to photoshop.  <br><br>I'd give it a try but I absolutely stink at all kinds of photo editing =).  Give it a shot <a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Fun&message.id=663#M663">here</a><br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Fri 03 Dec 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Wed 01 Dec 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="3878"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Weekly Exclusive Champions of Norrath: Return to Arms screenshot</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=3878>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=3878">Mail News</a></span><br>For the third week here's an exclusive screenshot from the upcoming PS2 Action-RPG "Champions of Norrath: Return to Arms".  <br><br><a href="screenshots/?ss=266"><img src="screenshots/thumb.php?ss=266" border=0></a><br><br>I'm sure that armor is some of the most protective in the game =).<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Wed 01 Dec 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Tue 30 Nov 2004</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="3838"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Changes coming to Tacvi</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=3838>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=3838">Mail News</a></span><br>The most talked about GoD zone is about to get <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=64356">some changes</a>:<blockquote>In the next update, tentatively scheduled for December 15th, some changes will be made to the Gates of Discord zone, Tacvi.  The zone will have increased loot drops and over a dozen new items added to its list. <br><br>We will also be changing the zone reset timer from 3 days to 5 days as some of the new items will be a bit more potent than those currently in the zone.<br><br>Go get your flags and be the first to find the new items.</blockquote><br>Should be fun to see what they do!<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Tue 30 Nov 2004</span><br><br><br><a name="3837"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">The Guide Program Needs You!</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=3837>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=3837">Mail News</a></span><br>Once again SOE has put out the call for new Volunteer Guides.  Here's the <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=64355">full post</a>.<blockquote>Hail and well met citizens of Norrath!<br><br>Do you travel the land seeking new challenges?  Do you wonder what it might be like to don a mask and adventure behind the scenes? Does the thought of entertaining others by telling a story or weaving an adventure appeal to you?<br><br>The EverQuest Guide Program is looking for more energetic individuals to help us bring more fun and adventure to Norrath. We're growing and changing and we can't do it alone. We need your help to bring more magic to the world of Norrath!<br><br>Ready to join us? Step forward and fill out an application today! <a href="https://guide.everquest.com/guideapp/">Guide Application</a></blockquote><br>If you think you can make EQ better for players here's your chance, be sure to check it out!<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Tue 30 Nov 2004</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--></center>
